", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700763}, {"id": 98600, "content": "无理由退换货", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 103977, "content": "放入购物车，每天看，看到不喜欢为止。剁手党奇招。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636775}, {"id": 103978, "content": "去实体店试完一定要上网上旗舰店看有没有优惠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130375}, {"id": 98603, "content": "习惯了色差。下单一件孔雀蓝买回来一看薄荷绿，评论“色差太大不过薄荷绿也挺喜欢的，收了” ", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 103979, "content": "无法买到合脚的鞋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700806}, {"id": 98604, "content": "必须成套买，网购回来的单品自己搭配怎么搭怎么丑 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 103980, "content": "淘宝。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461206}, {"id": 103981, "content": "在实体店看好了拍下型号去淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594373}, {"id": 98606, "content": "只关注收藏店铺上新，从不在淘宝上直接搜 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 297, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 103982, "content": "保险让生活更美好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700541}, {"id": 103983, "content": "保险让生活更美好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700541}, {"id": 103986, "content": "不淘宝买了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 621806}, {"id": 107063, "content": "一定是自己最喜欢的，可以陪自己很久越来越喜欢的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713334}, {"id": 103992, "content": "没什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324761}, {"id": 103993, "content": "每次都想买大一号", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700888}, {"id": 103995, "content": "分裂了，便宜的很便宜，贵的很贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623065}, {"id": 103997, "content": "向买过的人提问！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700971}, {"id": 103998, "content": "先看买家秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605591}, {"id": 104000, "content": "先看品牌，后看质量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529205}, {"id": 104001, "content": "年轻时总想淘到质量好还很便宜的，老了就不相信有物美价廉这回事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700988}, {"id": 104002, "content": "看完买家秀什么都不想买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698882}]}